Package: bitwarden-cli
Architecture: amd64
Depends: nodejs (>= 18), ${misc:Depends}
Description: command-line interface for Bitwarden password manager
 Bitwarden CLI is a powerful, full-featured command-line interface
 for interacting with a Bitwarden vault. It can be used in scripts
 and terminal workflows to manage passwords, secure notes, and
 other vault items.
 .
 Features include login/unlock, sync, list/get/create/edit/delete
 vault items, generate passwords, manage organizations, and
 import/export vault data.
